{
  "texts": [
    "Feng et al.",
    "demonstrated a fully printed MoS 2 memristor crossbar array, showing the existence of inter-layer grain boundaries in the printed MoS 2 film [34].",
    "Density functional theory (DFT) calculation and conductiveatomic force microscope (CAFM) confirmed the facilitating effect of grain boundaries on the migration of Ag atoms during filament formation and rupture.",
    "Additionally, Tang et al.",
    "revealed that the sulfur vacancies percolation along the flake edges of MoS 2 is able to further modulate the resistance switching behavior [90]."
  ]
}